, in this, once upon a time fresh position, there are 400 games already.   6...Nc6  is actually a potential transposition to the Rauzer variation of the Classical Sicilian.  7.Qd2  Bd7  8.O-O-O  e6  surely there will be a separate Chessable course on this one... }
